Much more powerful installer for bioinformatics tools (much more powerful than pip!)
Miniconda-conda-Setup Bioconda
after setting up chanel, install the software or package:

conda install bwa
conda create -n myenviroment bwa=0.7.12

for example to install pysam which is impossible for pip but for bioconda it is soooo easy:
conda install -c bioconda pysam (https://github.com/pysam-developers/pysam/issues/262)

reference links:
http://conda.pydata.org/miniconda.html
http://bioconda.github.io/
